{"tid":438742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【少女唔鋤愛阿婆】澳洲15歲男性侵84歲阿嬤　","createTime":"2017-10-17T08:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T16:18:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33457a9b2720298eb31b1a39ef77135cbd8ed20d","tid":438742,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171017/640_ffb326cf468327f758d31f49452d7e09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171017%2F640_ffb326cf468327f758d31f49452d7e09.jpg&h=64e283ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Waikiki的民宅。翻攝GOOGLE</span><br />\n<br />\n澳洲伯斯（Perth）近日發生一起可惡的入侵民宅案，一位阿嬤遭到了一名青少年的搶劫與性侵，還被迫在這名青少年面前洗澡。<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲新聞網》報導，本月13日清晨5點多，這名15歲的青少年，闖入了84歲阿嬤位於「威基基」（Waikiki）的家中，將還在睡覺的阿嬤，按到地上暴力性侵，過程中還將阿嬤打到重傷，並在性侵後，還強迫阿嬤洗澡洗掉證據。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，阿嬤後來被送醫急救，不久後出院，法醫也試圖在她家搜索，想得到這名青少年的DNA檢體。<br />\n<br />\n警方15日在一處民宅逮捕了一名青少年疑犯，將他送往西澳警局性侵調查科進行訊問。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171017/1223679/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171017%2F1223679%2F&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ko9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=3201f789\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171017/1223679/</a><br />\n<br />\n識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9677fdd76e81d853f6eb1a8aaf5a0a8813f9b6b","tid":438742,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"你婆婆好得喎"},{"pid":"d8df56c8576b56720bec374e2426e68f2fc730e9","tid":438742,"uid":117760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"關節酸痛咪玩咁癲"},{"pid":"2413c1bc1acace44ffcbedce2b90dc818163084c","tid":438742,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply